<div style="width: 740px; border: 1px dashed gray; padding: 10px;  margin:0px auto;">

<h2>IPD Patient Diagnosis</h2><hr />
<span class="title">Screen Overview </span><br />
This screen captures the patient working diagnosis details. Use can enter new diagnosis daily 
<br /><hr /><br />
<img src="images/IPD_patientdiagnosis.jpg" width="725"  /><br /><br />
<hr />

<p>

<span class="title">Patient Details:</span><br />
On clicking of discharge summary button user can access discharge summary for Obstetric and gynecology cases.
Based on patient selection from main screen patient details will display user can’t modify patient details.
<br />
<span class="title">Z03:</span> <br />
User can select Z03 it indicates this is new patient, it can remain blank.
 
<br />
  <span class="title">Z09:</span> 
    <br />User can select Z09 it indicates this is repeat patient, it can remain blank.
<br />
    <span class="title">Add Row (Button):</span> 
    <br />User wants to enter multiple diagnoses then user can add the new row it the grid.
<br />
    <span class="title">Delete Row (Button):</span> 
    <br />User can delete the row from the grid.
<br />
    <span class="title">Search (Button)</span> 
    <br />By clicking on search button user can search diagnosis either code or any description.
<br />
    <span class="title">ICD code: </span> 
    <br />User can write exact ICD code then diagnosis name will display in the grid, it can remain blank.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Diagnosis: </span> 
    <br />User can write diagnosis based on user entry in the diagnosis column, it can’t remain blank.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Provisional Diagnosis:</span> 
    <br />User can select whether it is provisional diagnosis or not 
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Final Diagnosis: </span> 
    <br />User can select whether it is final diagnosis or not .
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Previous Diagnosis:</span> 
    <br />User can view previous diagnosis against the admission number, user can’t change the diagnosis.
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Submit (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on Submit button user can save the data. 
    
    <br />
    <span class="title">Discharge Summary (Button):</span> 
    <br />By clicking on discharge summary button user can enter discharge details..
        
         
     <br />
    <span class="title">Back (Button):</span> 
    <br />Clicking on Back button, will move user to the previous screen.
       
</p>
</div>
